{"tid":1106953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"非洲國家深陷「一帶一路」財務陷阱      日本擬派專家救援","createTime":"2019-04-15T02:00:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-15T05:34:10.000Z","uid":184679,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3e6db58ecb54fd39d6af3efa9539d69d8942dee3","tid":1106953,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T02:00:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2019/04/15/phpKSsDRP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fbusiness%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F04%2F15%2FphpKSsDRP.jpg&h=400790d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國推展「一帶一路」，灑幣開路，非洲是重點區域之一，向非洲各國實施大量基建投資及借貸，如今，已使得多非洲國家陷入債務錢坑，據報導，日本政府決定派遣金融專家，救援非洲國家對中國的債務錢坑。<br />\n<br />\n《共同社》報導，日本政府擬在8月橫濱市舉行的非洲開發會議（TICAD）上正式提出，且是希望在8月的TICAD結束後馬上開始，目前，日方已展開向多個相關國家徵詢意向。<br />\n<br />\n據報導，日方作法是，派金融專家前往非洲國家，指導當地財政重建的經驗知識，不過，過程中將會對該國政府欠華債的情況，進行詳查，並提出償債建言，而此舉，而日本此舉明顯是想拉攏對中國抱有不滿的相關國家，以制衡中國一帶一路政策，同時提升日企在非洲國家的影響力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2759042\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2759042&d=pCiTPPmJHnjmYpxxI6xjveL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=eba59f50\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2759042&h=b7f24569\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2759042</a>"},{"pid":"8dde496cb44406355b3838c6107ed4edd8357e38","tid":1106953,"uid":209487,"like":1,"dislike":76,"score":-75,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T02:19:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"84fefdafde8f01ebfc1b0be3ca2b82183aab7b11","tid":1106953,"uid":55913,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T02:27:03.000Z","msg":"痴埋支那度都無好下場"},{"pid":"4cd0bed4fe95db12a9dd7f74f216023c241ae83f","tid":1106953,"uid":19296,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"quote":{"pid":"8dde496cb44406355b3838c6107ed4edd8357e38","tid":1106953,"uid":209487,"li